commit.title: [make] Amend "[dev. files] num → zarith"
commit.message:
[make] Amend "[dev. files] num → zarith"

As noted in the GitHub review, we need to include zarith in the core
system.

We should be able, as a nice side-effect, to remove the special build
rules for micromega, but not yet it seems.
